FROM (
    SELECT u.id, u.created_at, u.date_of_birth, u.email, u.fullname, u.is_verified, u.password_hash, u.phone_number, u.profile_id, u.role_permission_id, u.salt, u.updated_at, u.username
    FROM users AS u
    WHERE u.email = @__model_Email_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT u0.id, u0.role_id, u0.user_id, r.id AS id0, r.created_at, r.name, r.updated_at
    FROM user_roles AS u0
    INNER JOIN roles AS r ON u0.role_id = r.id
) AS s ON u1.id = s.user_id
ORDER BY u1.id, s.id
